-[ ] Migration tool: `KEEPCompact`/epoch-recompact path that emits OFS-only via GIT-002; run it over each shard (and document the one-shot for real `~/.be` stores) before flipping GIT-004 on.
-[ ] Crash recovery: on rw-open, if the log tail past the last `.idx` offset holds unindexed objects (or a torn append), re-`UNPK` the tail and re-flush; on a torn final object, truncate to the last whole object boundary.
